        "pf_4a60ef7f_value": "I seldom write reviews, but I felt compelled to write this one. I purchased this system last winter to help heat the family room that is always cold in the winter and hot in the summer. This system performed better than expected. It was an easy DIY installation. This summer I believe it has cut my electric bill by 1/3rd. It keeps the whole downstair cool and comfortable. I would and will buy another one.",
        "pf_5736c1ae_value": "🌟Here’s your chance to win a $1,000 e-gift card to spend on Della’s top-of-the-line heating and cooling products! Whether you’re in the market for a portable AC, a window air conditioner, or a mini-split system, this prize gives you the freedom to choose the perfect solution for your home or office.\n<br><br>⏰The contest runs from Nov. 25, 2024, 12:00 AM PST to Dec. 2, 2024, 11:59 PM PST. ",
        "pf_59fddbeb_value": "A1.All products on the dellahome.com are eligible for discounts. Mix and match freely to unlock Black Friday Deals!🔥<br><br>⏰<strong>From Nov.27 - Dec. 2</strong>⏰, enjoy Black Friday Deals.\n<br><br>&nbsp; 🎟️Black Friday Deals🎟️: Enjoy <strong>15% off</strong> all products sitewide.\n\nNo need to worry—the discount will be automatically applied at checkout.",
        "pf_a607f4f8_value": "Great Mini Split, would buy again so we did. I finished installing the second system and it works as well if not better than the first. I only needed our son's help to vacuum out the lines. We now have 2 cooling and heating our 32 ft 5th wheel trailer that is permanently set up in central Wisconsin, they work great!",
        "pf_3c24b761_value": "Installation was a two-person job. Performance-wise it works amazingly it keeps our very hot desert home cool as a cucumber. Appearance-wise very sleek. No leakage. It's a great size for a larger living room area! There's a remote or you can also control the unit from an app on your phone from anywhere.",
        "pf_8eda6701_value": "So far this unit is cooling my 600 sq ft house wonderfully. It has made my summer so much better before it has even started. It is so quiet and easy to control. It has been a total game-changer. I'm so glad I went this route instead of using my creepy hot air ducts for central AC.",
        "pf_9eeb8220_value": "This unit is amazing! It’s not only beautiful but also fits perfectly with my surroundings. The performance and quietness are impressive, quickly adjusting the room temperature to a comfortable level. I’m very satisfied with the service from Della as well.<br>",
        "pf_56173958_value": "A3. Dellahome usually takes one business day to arrange the shipping for your order. However,during the holiday season, you can expect your order to shipapproximately 2-3 business days after being placed. eu fugiat nulla pariatur.",
        "pf_f7b4c4d3_value": "This mini-split was so easy to set up! It has solid components and seems like it will last for years. It cools off my garage in minutes! I'm so pleased with my purchase! No more window units for me!",
        "pf_a44204b7_value": "My introduction into this technology proves superb with Della. I have yet to see the electric bill since adding the device and plan to purchase another unit if reasonable. For my needs it is great.",
        "pf_05cd9e0b_value": "Upgrade your cooking game with our 20-piece kitchen utensil set. Crafted from durable and heat-resistant materials, this set covers all your culinary needs. Elevate your kitchen experience today!",
